person's functioning,

00:11:19.840 --> 00:11:23.230
and medical, psychiatric,
environmental issues,

00:11:23.230 --> 00:11:26.590
and to come up with
recommendations and suggestions

00:11:26.590 --> 00:11:28.850
that would hopefully help the person

00:11:28.850 --> 00:11:30.503
